sql:
SELECT AVG(value) AS average_value
FROM variable_values
WHERE variable_id = 0;

SELECT variable_value_id, variable_id, value
FROM variable_values
WHERE quality_flag = 'good';

external_knowledge:
The top 3 sensors refer to those with the highest number of datasets generated; 
Average file size is a measure of the average size of all data files associated with each sensor's dataset; 
Unique users who have accessed the datasets from these sensors refer to distinct user IDs in the access logs.
